  <div class="blog-entry--body">
    <div class="blog-entry--body-first">
              <div class="d-none d-xl-block">
          
        </div>
          </div>
    <div class="blog-entry--body-second">
      <div class="blog_entry__key-points">
  <h3 class="blog_entry__key-points-title">Key points</h3>
  <ul class="blog_entry__key-points-item-list">
          <li class="blog_entry__key-points-item">Personal life experiences and personality differences predictably shape our political affiliations.</li>
          <li class="blog_entry__key-points-item">Many of my therapy sessions address relationship ruptures caused by political differences.</li>
          <li class="blog_entry__key-points-item">Bridging political divides and conflicts requires listening with the intent to understand others.</li>
      </ul>
</div>

            
